    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow all British Army servicemen to wear a beard",
        "additional_details": "With recruitment and retention at an all time low this small change could boost morale and be a demonstration that the army does listen to its soldiers.\r\n \r\nIt may be in the Government\u2019s interest for recruitment and retention in particular in these current times.\r\n \r\nIt should also make the Army feel more inclusive of current climate and fashion trends.",
        "background": "The Royal navy has allowed men to wear trimmed beards for years, the RAF has recently brought in amendments to allow servicemen to grow beards.",
